Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.59,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍將延續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.75,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜爛的世界
