Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.33,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟隨神風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.87,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向著未知之處前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.87,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的熱情與
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:14.07,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}薰染的靈魂勒緊胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.53,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃燒的火焰般
